Class RemoveLowOtuCounts

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BioModule, JavaModule, ScriptModule, Comparable<BioModule>

    public class RemoveLowOtuCounts
extends OtuCountModule
    This BioModule set low OTU counts below a configured threshold to zero.
    These low sample counts are assumed to be miscategorized or contaminents.
    GUI Module Name
    Remove Low OTU Counts
